   <S PAR='96' RSNT='1' SNO='96'>When we say this, we have the shining.</S>
   <S PAR='97' RSNT='1' SNO='97'>As the Lord deals with us time after time, we yield to Him time after time.</S>
   <S PAR='98' RSNT='1' SNO='98'>As we yield to Him in this way, our spirit becomes enlightened.</S>
