   <S PAR='101' RSNT='1' SNO='101'>The words we use in our preaching should be molded through the divine dealings and trials we experience; they should not be something conjured up by ourselves.</S>
   <S PAR='102' RSNT='1' SNO='102'>As a minister of the word, we have to make sure that we are making progress in our speaking.</S>
